The Telegraph - Calcutta : Business
 Wednesday, January 21, 2004 				 Morepen swap plan
																								New Delhi, Jan. 20 (PTI): The board of Morepen Laboratories today gave an in-principle nod to a proposal to convert fixed deposits to fully convertible debentures. This would provide an option to its 80,000 fixed deposit holders of the bulk drug maker to convert their deposit amount into fully convertible debentures and also receive reward by way of possible increase in the equity price.																								The proposal was finalised after seeking the views of the fixed deposit brokers and key financial institutions, a company release said. 
